'''''Kill or Be Killed''''' (bwa mbere yasohokeye muri [[Amerika]] nka '''''Karate Killer''''' irongera isohorerwa muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo nka  '''''Karate Olympiad''''' ) ni filime yasohotse muri 1977 muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo / [[Amerika]] karate film iyoborwa na Ivan Hall. Iyi filime yakorewe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo, iyi filime yiswe ''Kill cyangwa Be Killed'' muri [[Amerika]] mu 1980 kugira ngo yunguke menshi mu gukina filime z'ubuhanzi bw'intambara zo muri [[Amerika]]. 

