== Gufungura inguzanyo ==
Urukurikirane rwo kwamamara rugaragaza imiterere ya James Ryan Steve Hunt agerageza gukinira ikipe ya von Rudloff kandi ubwamamare burenze umubiri wa Ryan ahantu hose, usibye izina rya film.

== karate yo mubuyapani ==
Uburyo bwo kurwana muri film bwerekana uburyo bwiza bwa karate yu [[Buyapani]], tubikesha Ishyirahamwe rya Karate [[Ubuyapani|ry’Ubuyapani]] ([[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo). Shihans Stan Schmidt na Norman Robinson bakoze choreografi ya karate ya firime, ndetse banagaragara muri iyi filime nk'abanyamuryango babiri bagize ikipe ya karate ya von Rudloff.
